{"tid":1384924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於維繫香港自由鬥士的兵源和戰鬥力、持久力的問題","createTime":"2019-07-30T03:25:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T06:45:43.000Z","uid":8512,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cf6f386ec1bc00a879b6a1e51cc1bd264548039e","tid":1384924,"uid":8512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:25:39.000Z","msg":"陳雲：關於維繫香港自由鬥士（Hong Kong Freedom Fighters）的兵源和戰鬥力、持久力的問題。我想大家重溫一次光復香港戰役（Liberate Hong Kong）的政治定性、戰略定位及戰術。<br />\n一、政治定性：香港這次鬥爭，是全世界反中共、反法西斯、反政府監控人民的前線鬥爭，具有解放香港及解放世界的重大意義。全世界的人都應該支援香港人這場戰役。<br />\n二、戰略定位：這是人民戰爭，也是持久戰。愛護香港自由與憲政的香港人，不分階級、性別、年齡、族裔及地區，都應該投入這場有關香港生死存亡的戰役。投入的方法，各自按照自己的專長、財力和地區而定，即使不參與的市民，也要在必須的時候贊助、掩護及協助香港自由鬥士。<br />\n三、戰術：流水社運，游擊戰。無名無姓、無領袖、無大台、無佔領、無陣地，得到戰略目標之後便解散再來，前仆後繼，直至得到戰果為止。<br />\n四、戰果：香港普選，憲政民主，完全自治（與香港獨立一樣），不到此戰果，我們誓不罷休。普選之後的立法會必須通過法例或令到行政長官發告行政命令，取消撿控是次香港解放鬥爭的所有被捕平民，立即無條件釋放獄中所有香港自由鬥士（包括佔中五子、梁天琦及其他鬥士），給予充足之名譽恢復、就業安排、退休安排及金錢補償。另外依法逮捕是次自由鬥爭觸犯政府官員守則及警察守則之官員，懲罰協助政府虐待自由鬥士之公私法團。<br />\n（拜託各位協助廣傳，傳閱可以，口傳可以。使愈來愈多人知道和理解。必須持續宣傳，才可以變成人民戰爭的。）"},{"pid":"3c5807c694161d2ea2e6b5d7574ab040e0c4ac3e","tid":1384924,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:25:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推! 8月5罷工!!!!! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日(7月30)1500-2000</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">餓住的小朋友入一入黎, 有心幫佢地都可以黎睇下</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1382980/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1382980/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\nTG:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkrevolutiondocument&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrms3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=e578f375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument</a><br />\nFB:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%9B%B8-100576917956000/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%259B%25B8-100576917956000%2F&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrms3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=7cdc0a6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%9B%B8-100576917956000/</a>"},{"pid":"09c86e724ff09aa0bcaa4bd27fe8648c0a6aafb8","tid":1384924,"uid":8512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:27:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7474ae37b9bf086c64df9cbf55dce00c681c8e20","tid":1384924,"uid":8512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:27:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9b1d717b67ab62c696e8af189145369e493b71e","tid":1384924,"uid":8512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:31:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9366cda203736ef3dc13ead36eb7ef5020d1b5ff","tid":1384924,"uid":8512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:31:33.000Z","msg":"五"},{"pid":"dc9eeff419ac3e7d742b61d90f1a82abdd656624","tid":1384924,"uid":8512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:31:43.000Z","msg":"大"},{"pid":"e66329102ae841c7f3efb676aa55d4e5b79cc030","tid":1384924,"uid":8512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:31:53.000Z","msg":"訴"},{"pid":"462b9492cd8b90d68af892bbb1f2838e637b3ec7","tid":1384924,"uid":8512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:32:03.000Z","msg":"求"}